            <title>[LU-9182] interop: sanity_205 test failed sanity test_205: @@@@@@ FAIL: No jobstats for id.205.lfs.22059 found on mds2::*.lustre-MDT0001.job_stats</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9182</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;debug=-1


== sanity test 205: Verify job stats == 14:34:18 (1488791058)
Waiting 90 secs for update
Updated after 6s: wanted &apos;nodelocal&apos; got &apos;nodelocal&apos;
Registered as changelog user cl1
mdt.lustre-MDT0000.job_cleanup_interval=5
mdt.lustre-MDT0001.job_cleanup_interval=5
