 sanity test_205: @@@@@@ FAIL: No jobstats for id.205.lfs.31916 found on mds2::*.lustre-MDT0001.job_stats


&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Need to SKIP this test in case with interop&#160; where the -&lt;del&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5946&quot; title=&quot;jobstats are not expired if no new jobs arrive&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5946&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5946&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/del&gt;- is not present esp the changes around following in sanity/205 w.r.t. DNE&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;+       cmd=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;rmdir $DIR/$tdir&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
+       verify_jobstats &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$cmd&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$SINGLEMDS&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
+       # mkdir on secondary MDT
+       &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; [ $MDSCOUNT -gt 1 ]; then
+               cmd=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;lfs mkdir -i 1 $DIR/$tdir.remote&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
+               verify_jobstats &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$cmd&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;mds2&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
+       fi

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
